Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.07,0:35:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. You have a bal\Nyeah
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.59,0:35:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah yeah. So Gabe uh tuned me into what\Nwas happening and I began to read about
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.83,0:36:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it and pay attention to it and I said I\Ncan't believe uh and I know other
