Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.44,0:36:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to uh so all right so that's why we have\Nthis send your kids to my college
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.96,0:36:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all right so the\Nthere's reality in risk external and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.00,0:36:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,rest internal\Nnow the world as it is is unknown by the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.48,0:36:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,mind.\NWhy? Because
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.20,0:36:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,information is instantly processed in\None 10,000th of a second. In one
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.32,0:36:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,10,000th of a second. That's why it's so\Nhard to become enlightened. all the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.11,0:36:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,programs, all the feelings, all the\Nthings you've learned, all your belief
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.48,0:36:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,systems,\Nuh your style of uh contextualizing,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.28,0:36:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,your style of understanding and\Nintellectualizing, etc. All of this
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.48,0:37:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,happens in one 10,000th of a second.\NHow can you experience what is then? How
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.40,0:37:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,can you see? How can you ever experience\Nrest externa
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.48,0:37:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're stuck in rest internal?\NThe distance between them is one
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.35,0:37:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,10,000th of a second.\NH
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.00,0:37:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,how can you then escape being the slave\Nand the captive of the ego and it's all
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.68,0:37:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,all of its aversions and attractions\Netc. How can you get past that one
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.64,0:37:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,10,000th of a second?\NWell, people used to believe and they
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.52,0:37:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,still do that enlightenment is the space\Nbetween two thoughts. the Buddha taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.00,0:37:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I It's a mistransation of the Buddha\NBuddha. I never did get to the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.35,0:37:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Buddha thought throughout the\Ncenturies has been that um reality is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.11,0:37:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,glimpsed between two thoughts, between\Ntwo thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.88,0:37:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh you can't glimpse it between two\Nthoughts because the mind works faster
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.96,0:38:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,than one 10,000 of a second. So by the\Ntime you notice there's a gap there, you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.52,0:38:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer have a gap there. So it's like\Na dog chasing its tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.92,0:38:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can move your point\Nof observation faster than the rate of
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.59,0:38:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,mentation of the mind itself. You have\Nto move faster than 1 10,000 of a
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.56,0:38:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,second. That's why practically no one\Never gets enlightened. 1 and 10,000 of a
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.80,0:38:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,second because you cannot move faster.\NIt takes you one 10,000th of a second
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.83,0:38:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,then to look for the space between the\Ntwo thoughts and by that time the space
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.44,0:38:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is gone. There's no way you can become\Nenlightened by looking for the infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.35,0:38:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,silent formless space between two\Nthoughts. It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.48,0:38:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha is alleged to have said that,\Nbut he told me personally it's BS.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.72,0:38:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we've already talked about it in\Nthese previous lectures. The infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.80,0:39:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,silent space is not between two\Nthoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.24,0:39:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's below the thoughts. It's not on the\Nsurface of the sea. It's not like one
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.32,0:39:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,wave chasing another and you're going to\Nfind a place between the waves. No, the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.04,0:39:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,silence and the stillness is below the\Nmind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.04,0:39:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've spoken of this before. So as a\Nstyle of contemplation what you do is
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.04,0:39:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you disconnect from the particularity\Nuh the linearity of the worldly
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.92,0:39:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,phenomena\Nand you become awareness. You become the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.52,0:39:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,field of awareness. So you move from\Nparticipant experiencer
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.80,0:39:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,uh back to witness uh to observer.\NThen you you get that the only reason
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.88,0:39:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you're able to witness or observe is\Nbecause there is a infinite formless
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.07,0:39:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,field and you move back. The sense of\Neye moves from out there or what people
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.44,0:40:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,think of you out there or what's said\Nout there or what you believe out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.68,0:40:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It moves and you realize the one thing\Nthat doesn't change is the witness. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.11,0:40:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,always the same witnesser. No matter\Nwhat you can be a Democrat one year and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.88,0:40:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,10 years later be a Republican, but the\Nwitnesser doesn't say. So you I am that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.00,0:40:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which I am the witnesser. I'm the\Nwitnesser of the phenomena as they go
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.88,0:40:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,through the mind. Then you become even\Nmore sophisticated. You realize that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.44,0:40:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you are prior to witnessing because\Nwitnessing can happen of its own. But
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.64,0:40:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,how does one know that witnessing is\Neven happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.40,0:40:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There is therefore something more a\Npriority,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.24,0:40:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,more fundamental\Nto the witness and that is consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.72,0:40:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,itself.\NSo the sense of self moves from the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.11,0:40:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,individual ego, the narcissistic ego all\Nabout me and I and my tube and YouTube
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.72,0:41:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that.\NIt says the mind begins to say that's
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.64,0:41:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,boring BS. That's really a lot of BS out\Nthere. And it withdraws its interest
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.16,0:41:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,from that. And then it says, "How do I\Nknow anything?"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.72,0:41:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it says, "Well, who is the\Neye?" I mean, who is the eye that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.96,0:41:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,believes things?\NThe I believe this then and it believes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.28,0:41:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,this now. Is it a different eye?\NSo, you begin to find something that is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.40,0:41:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,always present. What is always present?\NAnd you will finally end up as you in
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.64,0:41:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,deep meditation\Nuh you let go all of attachments and
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.80,0:41:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,aversions. If you let go of attachments\Nand aversions and all thinkingness yes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.20,0:41:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and all ideiation and all symbolism and\Nall the stuff that goes on in the in the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.20,0:41:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,mind uh you end up with awareness\Nitself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.76,0:42:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But that which I am is no different than\Nawareness. But that in itself then
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.48,0:42:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes a belief system does it not?\NTherefore when lets go even the thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.44,0:42:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,or the belief of self as experiencer as\Nthe consciousness out of which
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.59,0:42:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,experiencing arises\Nand the identity between the self and
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.11,0:42:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that which\Nis the substrate of the self.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.92,0:42:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,then suddenly disappears.\NSuddenly disappears and as it disappears
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.59,0:42:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel yourself die.\NSo people write me periodically they
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.96,0:42:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,feel they're dying. I say good wonderful\Nbecause that which you really are cannot
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.59,0:42:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,die. So what you're experiencing is the\Ndeath of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.11,0:43:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens then is the mind becomes\Nprogressively silent. And then you're in
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.52,0:43:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,nonlinear realms, nonlinear realms, not\Nwithin mind itself. You're in realms of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.92,0:43:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,much greater dimension. The these are\Nthe realms of context, not of content.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.16,0:43:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the beginning, you think of self\Nin terms of content. I am me. I'm 62
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.48,0:43:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,years old, etc.\NThen finally you you begin to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.96,0:43:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,self as context. I'm the context out of\Nwhich arises awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.04,0:43:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,believingness witnessing etc.\NAnd you begin to move farther and
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.44,0:43:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,farther back and then you will come to\Nwhat I would call experientially it was
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.72,0:43:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,like a high pristine place. It was like\Num being in the top of the highest
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.88,0:44:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,mountain. So the highest Andes\Ncompletely
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.72,0:44:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,altitude is the closest analogy.\NUm infinite silence, nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.76,0:44:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing there, no nothing.\NThere is no one to experience anything
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.52,0:44:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there. And you go through the void. Uh\Nthe void is at calibration level 850.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.88,0:44:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the level confronting this\Nentity at age three.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.11,0:44:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Came out of oblivion into nothingness\Nand confronted with is the ultimate
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.52,0:44:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,reality allness or nothingness.\NAnd that took uh decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.96,0:44:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when you feel like you're dying,\Nthat's terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.31,0:44:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When you feel like you're dying, when\Nyour whole mind is silenced, it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.76,0:44:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,disappeared.\NWhen you feel yourself die, because you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.35,0:45:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,feel yourself die, it's not a belief\Nsystem.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.96,0:45:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you are\Ndissolves and
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.76,0:45:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you feel the self die. And I will tell\Nyou it is for a few moments
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.31,0:45:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,uh in extreme agony. All that you ever\Nthought you were, believed you were,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.88,0:45:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,experienced yourself were through all\Nthe lifetimes, zillions of lifetimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.11,0:45:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you're letting it go.\NThen you realize to reach enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.28,0:45:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,this too, oh Lord, I must give up till\Nyou leave. You give up everything, one
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.56,0:45:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,thing after another, desires and wishes\Nand aversions and thoughts and belief
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.11,0:45:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,systems,\Npolitics, religion, etc. You give it all
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.28,0:45:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,up to find the ultimate reality.\NThe last thing you're holding back is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.64,0:46:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,life. So then came the experience\Nand I realized that this too, oh Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.04,0:46:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,must I lay down to thee.\NAnd
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.35,0:46:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,then there is a moment of agony in which\Nyou feel yourself actually die and you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.68,0:46:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,do die because that which you think is\Nyou
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.31,0:46:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is what's dying. And if it was the real\Nyou, no nothing would be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.59,0:46:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The real you dies. It's taking the big\Njump that's leaping off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.44,0:46:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said to thee, oh Lord, I surrender\Nmy life. And then came the agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.31,0:46:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the agony stopped.\NAnd then ecstasy beyond all description.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.35,0:46:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, the world was reborn and radiated\Nforth the divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.16,0:47:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and the incredible beauty of all that\Nexists
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.88,0:47:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time and the reality\Nof your own and you run that is what's
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.80,0:47:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,called yo mystical\Nthe
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.80,0:47:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,god within god imminent etc.\NThen life is totally transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.56,0:47:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,experientially and in its meaning etc.\NYeah. So that is the ultimate reality
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.04,0:47:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is no reality.\NThere is no reality to become, to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.88,0:47:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,refuse, to ignore\Nthat which is and that which you are one
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.40,0:47:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the same.\NAnd
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.92,0:47:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the the the thing that marks it as the\Nultimate reality
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.48,0:48:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is its stunning beauty,\Nbut it's stunning love. The most
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.64,0:48:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,staggering thing about a after going\Nthrough this high pass of absolute
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.80,0:48:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,voidness\Nall of a sudden the earth shone forth
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.20,0:48:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with an incredible beauty\Nthat you the mind is silent in in the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.48,0:48:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,witnessing of the incredible beauty and\Nyou see the the essence of all things
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.28,0:48:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,shine forth. The presence of God as the\Nessence of all that exists shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.11,0:48:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you all all you see is divinity\Nwherever you look. Huh? which pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.07,0:48:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,much takes you out of operating in the\Nworld
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.07,0:48:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,uh for quite a while actually.\NThen if karmically
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.11,0:48:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,karmically uh predestined or not\Npredestined but destined as a capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.80,0:48:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,one might return to the world and speak\Nof such matters but it's totally
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.28,0:48:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,unnecessary.\NThat which is hardly needs you to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.44,0:49:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,validate that that which is is the\Nultimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.83,0:49:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hardly needful of you to attest to\Nit.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.24,0:49:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However, in a group like this, we have\Nmany strange people
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.92,0:49:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,who wish to reach enlightenment.\NOh boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.48,0:49:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what an exciting and wonderful journey\Nit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.00,0:49:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How exciting and wonderful it is. You\Nmove one paradigm of reality onto a a
