Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.28,1:22:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sexism. Ism. The minute you add ism to\Nanything, it come down comes down to
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.12,1:22:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,180. It's already down to 180.\NSo anything can be depicted by throwing
