Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.12,1:23:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See? So you can see how you can mix\Nmetaphors, mix
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.40,1:23:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,uh and editorialize and completely lose\Nthe reality of it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.48,1:23:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What does a man feel in his heart when\Nhe stands in respect to the woman? What
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.52,1:23:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,does he feel in his heart? Huh?\Nwoman.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.23,1:23:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I don't know.\N>> You know what's in the heart. Yes. So
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.92,1:23:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway, I just wanted to use that as an\Nexample how and of course this
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.52,1:23:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,indoctrination goes on subtly all day\Nround the clock in all various forms
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.19,1:23:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,including academia etc. in which\Neverything in society can be politicized
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.28,1:23:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,into perpetrator victim.\NEven integrity and honesty itself, even
