Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.60,1:24:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So indoctrination trumps reality.\NAs Bush said, money and oil trumps
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.44,1:24:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,reality, doesn't he?\NDid he say no? No. What he said is money
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.04,1:24:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,trumps peace or oil trumps peace. That\Ncalibrates at 365.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.67,1:24:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Bush said it. Money or oil, I\Nforget. Trump's peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.19,1:24:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Functionally. Functionally.\NAll right. Narcissism therefore warps
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.67,1:24:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and distorts.\NEverything gets politicized.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.08,1:24:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,narcissistically warped and distorted so\Nthat it's self-s serving and it's always
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.19,1:24:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,self-s serving the perpetrator victim\Nrole
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.28,1:24:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the reason people cling to it is\Nthey love to picture themselves as
