Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.40,1:28:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is no calibrated level of a\Nthousand. There is no such thing as the
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.19,1:28:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,absolute. We have one more chart on\Nthis. Uh yes. Mhm. All right. So,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.92,1:28:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,absolutism is anathema\Nto relativist.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.28,1:28:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It just ruins their sleep and everything\Nelse. They can't eat nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.15,1:28:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Their life comes to an end\Nthat there is an absolute truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.56,1:28:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it make them so bad mad?\Nis because the narcissistic core of the
