Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.63,1:28:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So the narcissistic core of the ego\Nhates divinity and it hates the
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.96,1:29:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,absolute. It hates calibrated levels of\Nconsciousness. Yeah. It hates that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.63,1:29:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,just hates that.\NThe fact that a dog calibrates higher
