Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.60,1:29:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it say?\NReality is a product of paradigms. Oh,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.71,1:29:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,yes.\NNot only is reality difficult if not
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.40,1:29:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,impossible to ascertain,\Nevery paradigm of reality has is a
