Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.71,1:31:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Minutes left.\N>> Well, I'll hurry up. I'll hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.00,1:31:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You notice women are not repressed. I\Nmean, all it's just do is raise her
