Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.15,1:32:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Repressed women. Yeah. Right.\NIn their imagination.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.52,1:32:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They like to play victim.\NSo, the narcissistic ego loves to be
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.52,1:32:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,victim. Loves to be victim. Yeah. Well,\Nuh, tell you what, there's not better
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.48,1:32:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that way either.\NWe said that all reality is presumptive
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.48,1:32:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,versus provable. Uh, you can't prove any\Nreality whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.15,1:32:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mark said religion is the opiate of the\Npeople. Wonder people wonder why
