Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.08,1:33:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Relativistic antagonism\Ntowards the absoluteism of religion.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.40,1:33:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See? All right.\NTolerance is a very fashionable world a
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.52,1:33:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,word\Nand it's really a downward slope to
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.48,1:33:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,non-reality\Nbecause tolerance is now applied to
