Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.76,1:33:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tolerant to everything.\NSo I suggest you're welcome to be
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.56,1:34:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,tolerant to anything you like.\NBut don't include me in.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.67,1:34:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because a kimod dragon is still a\Nkomodo dragon.
