Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.92,1:38:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,member of the oct octagenarians of which\NI am president
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.00,1:38:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is a sense of humor.\NA sense of humor about anything and
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.11,1:38:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,everything. See, a sense of humor is\Nnecessary for longevity.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.08,1:38:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All the people who lack it are probably\Nsix feet under already because they took
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.52,1:38:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,everything seriously. Yeah. I used to\Ntake things seriously. Well, I told you
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.48,1:38:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,how I did. I had to go for treatment for\Nscupulosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.19,1:38:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother would call up to the bedroom.\NShe'd say, "Are you dressed, ready to go
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.88,1:38:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,yet?" And I'd say, "Yes, mom. I'll be\Nright down." I still had one sock and
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.96,1:38:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,one shoe to put on. I said, "Yes, mom.\NI'll be right down." I quickly put them
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.36,1:38:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,on. I run down the stairs. Instantly,\NI'm hit with guilt that I lied to my
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.04,1:38:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,mother.\N>> She said, "Are you ready to go?" And I
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.15,1:38:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,said, "Yes, and I still had one shoe and\None sock." So, literally, it was a lie,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.36,1:38:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,right?\NWell, I'd have that guilt until I got to
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.96,1:39:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,confession.\N10 Hail Marys and five our fathers.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.60,1:39:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the priest would say, you know,\Nyou don't need to feel guilty about
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.80,1:39:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,every little trivial thing. So\Nyeah, the other side of no conscience is
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.48,1:39:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,too much conscience,\Nscrupulosity. So a sense of humor
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.92,1:39:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,prevents scrupulosity\Nbecause I want everybody to take
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.36,1:39:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,everything spiritually seriously, but\Nnot to the point of scrupulosity and
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.88,1:39:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,still have a sense of humor about it.\NYes. Okay. What happens next?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.67,1:39:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> We uh take a quick break.\N>> Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.76,1:39:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> And then we'll line up for question and\Nanswers.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.92,1:39:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh, we take a quick break\Nand then we'll have questions and
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.32,1:39:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,answers and then after that I get to\Nshake everybody's hand. Oh, good. Okay,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.19,1:40:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that sounded like a jolly afternoon.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.44,1:40:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
